{"tid":458880,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"劇場版Fate/kaleid liner 魔法少女☆伊莉雅 雪下的誓言 集中討論","createTime":"2017-11-05T09:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T18:32:25.000Z","uid":3020,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"f05ee433158c43e3428cfca40690f6144502a924","tid":458880,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:42:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TzjnmiJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTzjnmiJ.jpg&h=8848eee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡介<br />\n「首先，就由我這邊來先說起。我與美遊&hellip; 至今為止的故事」<br />\n<br />\n世界正邁向滅亡。想要阻止，就只能犧牲身為「聖杯」的美遊。<br />\n是世界？還是美遊？<br />\n對於打著「拯救世界」名義的恩茲華斯所拋出的問題，伊莉雅的回答是「兩邊都救」。<br />\n<br />\n戰鬥結束之後迎來短暫的休息。伊莉雅一行人被士郎邀請到自己的家中。之後眾人聚集在一起，由士郎開始陳述他和美遊的過往。<br />\n美遊是能無差別地實現願望的神稚兒。士郎將無處可去的她帶回到他與切嗣所共同居住的家。<br />\n從那之後過了五年，兩人就像是真正的兄妹一樣過著和平的生活。<br />\n<br />\n但是，那樣的日常生活突然間就宣告結束。<br />\n來到美遊所出生的老家的兩人，渴求著美遊的「奇蹟」的朱利安出現在兩人的面前&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n美遊與士郎以及恩茲華斯的因緣，在此揭曉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n＜STAFF＞<br />\n原作：ひろやまひろし ．TYPE-MOON<br />\n監督：大沼心<br />\n腳本：井上堅二、水瀬葉月<br />\n角色設定：平田和也<br />\n音樂：加藤達也．TECHNOBOYS PULCRAFT GREEN-FUND<br />\n音樂製作：Lantis<br />\n主題曲歌手：ChouCho<br />\n動畫製作：SILVER LINK.<br />\n配給：角川 ANIMATION<br />\n製作：「劇場版プリズマ☆イリヤ」製作委員会<br />\n<br />\n＜CAST＞<br />\n衛宮 士郎：杉山紀彰<br />\n朔月 美遊：名塚佳織<br />\n伊莉雅絲菲爾．馮．愛因茲貝倫：門脇舞以<br />\n一義 樹里庵：花江夏樹<br />\n間桐 櫻：下屋則子<br />\n衛宮 切嗣：小山力也<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPV<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0W2RrFEt6Sc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0W2RrFEt6Sc&d=HuWeHQR%2B9bk7sVdwjCzc59tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=4b159909\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0W2RrFEt6Sc</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M2ApQrCn_AY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DM2ApQrCn_AY&d=HuWeHQR%2B9bk7sVdwjCzc59tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=d60895e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M2ApQrCn_AY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n線上<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://myself-bbs.com/thread-43321-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyself-bbs.com%2Fthread-43321-1-1.html&d=HuWeHQR%2B9bk7sVdwjCzc59tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=1235ca2a\" target=\"_blank\">http://myself-bbs.com/thread-43321-1-1.html</a></div>"},{"pid":"8e769540868a56d25ba5413e6e6c979927a31edd","tid":458880,"uid":3020,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T10:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a37bc500b70078470429b977190c5f730e5c5a6","tid":458880,"uid":31641,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T10:52:42.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇完<br />\n雖然幾好睇,但真係經費不足同埋漫畫畫得太好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好難比得上"},{"pid":"370a2e54f5b725df6c5b614ba393e5c312f9907d","tid":458880,"uid":93595,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T11:07:34.000Z","msg":"竟然可以係伊莉雅劇場版見到伊莉雅<br />\n好感動"},{"pid":"5706658900fe9e2e7df07f6a416640bcfccbb128","tid":458880,"uid":118314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:05:11.000Z","msg":"咩話<br />\n呢套野有伊莉雅!? <br />\n10/10分"},{"pid":"8558b221731a9869c2c5e7a8703f8de022fe84ae","tid":458880,"uid":144944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:11:35.000Z","msg":"衛宮巨俠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n型到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我愛士郎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bda5c3e1da4cc99e805fa64da7fe4f4af696400","tid":458880,"uid":8307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:14:36.000Z","msg":"衛宮大俠傳"},{"pid":"100d39860001c3fca0c7563cd39f0bde34560445","tid":458880,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:36:2