":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T19:13:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I am the bone of my sword.<br />\n(体は剣で出来ている。)<br />\nSteel is my body, and fire is my blood.<br />\n(血潮は鉄で、心は硝子。)<br />\nI have created over a thousand blades.<br />\n(幾たびの戦場を越えて不敗。)<br />\nUnaware of beginning.<br />\n(たった一度の敗走もなく、)<br />\nNor aware of the end.<br />\n(たった一度の勝利もなし。)<br />\nStood pain with inconsitent weapons.<br />\n(遺子はまた独り)<br />\nMy hands will never hold anything.<br />\n(剣の丘で細氷を砕く)<br />\n――――yet,<br />\n(けれど、)<br />\nmy flame never ends.<br />\n(この生涯はいまだ果てず)<br />\nMy whole body was<br />\n(偽りの体は、)<br />\nstill<br />\n(それでも)<br />\n&ldquo;unlimited blade works&rdquo;<br />\n(剣で出来ていた――――！！)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三種銘文入面，呢個最撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfd22c7fe2814dfc97591929b08e16bb905d949","tid":458880,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T19:27:28.000Z","msg":"當年紅a單挑b叔7條命 <br />\n<br />\n開無限劍制個時講左句灑 無畏地戰鬥吧 型到仆街"},{"pid":"100f7cc24fa9a05b0e8d6178b4391fdf995ff53b","tid":458880,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:01:36.000Z","msg":"終於有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e246d9c36ec4c5427c30f4113be97ba230efd5","tid":458880,"uid":8082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T04:07:27.000Z","msg":"崩到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n金閃閃王財射唔中插落地果陣毫無力量感 似被人打飛把野跌落地<br />\n<br />\n真係開住聲睇漫畫算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983c3a9e2101674dd4f2e3c318b1041bbd0bd714","tid":458880,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T04:29:32.000Z","msg":"真係幾撚崩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\